name: Sexy Fish Stew
description: This rich and creamy fish and potato stew is easy to make in advance. You can simply add the fish when you reheat the soup.

name: Crispy Fish
description: A fried fish with a spicy and flavorful coating.

name: Sweet Potato Pie I
description: For this lovely pie, sweet potatoes are boiled, peeled and mashed together with butter, sugar, milk and eggs, then seasoned with nutmeg, cinnamon and vanilla.
